snippet.title: Galaxy Ranger (1983 Sega (Midway License))
snippet.description:
A Shooting 'em up game where fly through the universe battling alien ships to make your way to fight the main Alien Battle Cruiser. Along the way, you fly across alien deserts, through tunnels, over alien cities, and get involved in a few "astro-dogfights" with enemy space fighters.

This game plays very similar to Ashtron Belt.

Emulator: Daphne 1.00v win32
Recorder: Fraps
Editor: Virtual Dub
Encoder: Avisynth + Megui
